[{"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7577939245307970317", "createTime": 1764376494, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-29T00:34:54.000Z", "text": "i bought it today thinking i was gonna have a fun time but genuinely the game catalog is so tiny there’s no big titles and you have to pay a 89$ subscription for a year just for like 20 games its more for very little kids", "diggCount": 1, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "7435823660244501550", "uniqueId": "bootychecks47", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/e71ca22aa401fbe73c5e2dfad5f5c1fa~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=81fae88a&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=ltD50tVB3gjLJKf5hRShOBQnBRM%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我今天买了，想着会玩得很开心，但说实话游戏库太小了，没啥大作，而且一年89美元的订阅费才给20来个游戏，更适合非常小的孩子"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7579807849871393567", "createTime": 1764811566, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-04T01:26:06.000Z", "text": "Worth it. So tired of people pointing out the subscription. The yearly subscription = two switch games or one ps5 game 😭😭", "diggCount": 4, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 2, "uid": "6790000374297199622", "uniqueId": "goldheartedd_", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast8-avt-0068-tx2/da5b447eb6152ad70d54bd92763e890f~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=5e3207f7&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=bLYvuaiIoE3l3g911DyO1eRwRYg%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "值得。太厌倦别人指出订阅问题了。年订阅费=两款Switch游戏或一款PS5游戏 😭😭"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7579653881358254861", "createTime": 1764775711, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-03T15:28:31.000Z", "text": "We just got ours with the subscription. I think it depends on a few things, your kids, their ages, and what they like to do. We had a lot of fun with it the first night. I also am a working mom and really struggle to find time to work out. after bedtime I did some workouts thst got my body moving and made We sweat. I am competitive so the point feature of the workout I did was really motivating.", "diggCount": 1, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "6773848014894253062", "uniqueId": "htx2813308004", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/889fbc642d7c60a8b3ffe65d3a84bf6d~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=40dd2083&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=sAV6N%2BOuERntuHh0YmLt65BWt90%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我们刚买了带订阅的。我觉得这取决于几个因素，你的孩子，他们的年龄，以及他们喜欢做什么。我们第一天玩得很开心。我还是个职场妈妈，很难找到时间锻炼。睡着以后，我做了一些让我身体动起来并且出汗的锻炼。我很有竞争力，所以我做的锻炼的点数功能真的很有激励作用。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7577833850396689182", "createTime": 1764351958, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-28T17:45:58.000Z", "text": "I’ve been wondering too!! Was thinking about getting it for my 8 and 11yr olds for Christmas.", "diggCount": 3, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "7008666931234997253", "uniqueId": "handh.photos", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast8-avt-0068-tx2/c40409aae67756354532cc77ced3b273~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=ff6d52a0&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=G2OAMFH%2Bmv%2FbsIE78792bQBobiE%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我也一直在想！！想着圣诞节给我的 8 岁和 11 岁的孩子买一个。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7578027630626652959", "createTime": 1764397083, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-29T06:18:03.000Z", "text": "I got it and set it up early. We got the subscription for 3 months as our “trial” .. kids have played it all day the last 2 days. Really good and interactive, for the whole family too. Not just games geared towards kids.", "diggCount": 1, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "166427492394692608", "uniqueId": "sammpolmann", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-maliva-avt-0068/b5c11ea29a349d44bbac93970b1a5a4d~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=2d637c2a&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=tZBer4ztR%2FuBtTfHKN8mlIwnHYI%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我买了，并且提前设置好了。我们买了 3 个月的订阅作为我们的“试用期”……孩子们过去两天玩了一整天。真的很好玩，互动性也很强，适合全家。不只是给孩子玩的游戏。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7578544734268965645", "createTime": 1764517466, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-30T15:44:26.000Z", "text": "I just got it today from walmart. 199.99.", "diggCount": 1, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 1, "uid": "6796850782769726470", "uniqueId": "makaylahatchell", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/eef2c0cb6a7b313880a7020961d66e75~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=07592e79&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=EwvFsVFdS7FOCYavi2tBbRSdCcw%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我今天刚从 Walmart 买的。199.99。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7577850327287972663", "createTime": 1764355789, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-28T18:49:49.000Z", "text": "Guess I’ll find out I ordered it today", "diggCount": 2, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "7076573716255769646", "uniqueId": "mforeside210", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/cf90f6d3c277d2d2f3000594bbe34135~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=eaa31765&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=K1XIvrkpwJXUpAIDTCrhoMtEUdw%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "我想我今天下单了，到时候就知道了"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7578602952294859550", "createTime": 1764531029, "createTimeISO": "2025-11-30T19:30:29.000Z", "text": "It isn’t worth anything at all. I highly recommend an Xbox 360 Kinect or a Wii", "diggCount": 2, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "7372746379720606766", "uniqueId": "tarantulaballs71", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast8-avt-0068-tx2/cde859e94660681937c1b8b09ac9235f~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=4904aa7c&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=v2ChFJIWaacXCz2L%2BJGN%2Fi5R2lM%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "这玩意儿根本不值。我强烈推荐Xbox 360 Kinect或者Wii"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7580388782043333431", "createTime": 1764946837, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-05T15:00:37.000Z", "text": "No it’s not just buy a switch for your kids and you don’t need a subscription you just buy the games outright and keep them forever", "diggCount": 0, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "6665131097142476805", "uniqueId": "pp_idk", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/beb4fdac97576383fccfc5e584173319~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=20b6a2f1&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=OHGU5x68VXT0cA8d4y%2BwB31slN4%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "不，不是这样的，给孩子买个 Switch 就行了，你不需要订阅，直接买游戏，永远拥有。"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7579529811984597790", "createTime": 1764746896, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-03T07:28:16.000Z", "text": "Bought it today haven’t played it yet but so far from the reviews I’ve seen most people are saying it’s pretty fun, also I bought a 3 month gaming pass for my son as well instead of the full year in case it’s not worth it", "diggCount": 1, "likedByAuthor": true, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "6928439280609543174", "uniqueId": "key.shaauna", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/9b2bb1612a7ea70509c620bc552c4732~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=48723f3e&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=dLBIN2%2FmWAV4%2Bn3ZiDME%2BENV86Q%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "今天买了，还没玩，但看评论说大多数人都觉得挺好玩的，而且我给我儿子买了3个月的游戏通行证，而不是一年的，万一不值呢"}, {"videoWebUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "submittedVideoUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "input": "https://www.tiktok.com/@chynawayne1/video/7577830197144145183", "cid": "7578700173514982158", "createTime": 1764553658, "createTimeISO": "2025-12-01T01:47:38.000Z", "text": "What they’re not saying is that on top of the price, it’s $100 a year to play.", "diggCount": 2, "likedByAuthor": false, "pinnedByAuthor": false, "repliesToId": null, "replyCommentTotal": 0, "uid": "6789826923666408454", "uniqueId": "aphrojite", "avatarThumbnail": "https://p16-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tos-useast5-avt-0068-tx/e50f11fc7f78b8be2f39b91a362bc0e8~tplv-tiktokx-cropcenter:100:100.jpg?dr=9640&refresh_token=4d861026&x-expires=1775754000&x-signature=jw%2F7mfyy37NVhjLOQ%2Faibf3dTbE%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=30310797&shcp=ff37627b&idc=useast8", "mentions": [], "detailedMentions": [], "text_zh": "他们没说的是，除了这个价格，一年还要100美元才能玩。"}, {"vi